The paper discusses proposals for extracting data from tables encoded using HTML, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and computer vision techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Deep Learning (cs.DL), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
